{"tid":699980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 獄中親繪笑臉報平安　游蕙禎：不用擔心","createTime":"2018-06-13T03:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T08:22:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d0ce108e723a3d3fcec3e35c0cda09936d9f35","tid":699980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"前年當選立法會議員、後因宣誓風波而失去議席的青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎，早前因強衝入立法會會議廳案，被裁判官判囚4星期。其中游蕙禎放棄上訴，即時入獄服刑。其Facebook專頁昨晚上載一張游蕙禎親繪的「笑臉」信件，向外界報平安，指自己適應到，著支持者毋需擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/112907_443c8098bfbce44a01b8c7e01dae3e7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F112907_443c8098bfbce44a01b8c7e01dae3e7a.png&h=aac507ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/112909_9cc6020e7232b98b3c3619ae0321f910.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F112909_9cc6020e7232b98b3c3619ae0321f910.png&h=04df905e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其Facebook專頁昨日上載一張由游蕙禎於本月6日，即入獄後第3天的信件，信中內容未有太多文字敘述自身情況，但就繪上了8個大小不一，咧嘴而笑的笑臉，向外界報平安。信中寫到「各位：I am fine（我很好）。不用擔心，我適應到。有咩下個月我親身出黎講」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/198657/衝擊立法會-獄中親繪笑臉報平安-游蕙禎-不用擔心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F198657%2F%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E8%A6%AA%E7%B9%AA%E7%AC%91%E8%87%89%E5%A0%B1%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89-%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E-%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B69tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1eaf90aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/198657/衝擊立法會-獄中親繪笑臉報平安-游蕙禎-不用擔心</a>"},{"pid":"0ca6972353feb65e6741d026f963bd572f11d3a4","tid":699980,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"有 photo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"